# Files that must NOT be uploaded to / built by Vercel.
#
# Vercel treats every non-underscore `.js` file under /api as its own Serverless
# Function. The `*.test.js` files here are vitest suites — they import the
# `vitest` devDependency and are NOT HTTP endpoints. Deploying them is both wrong
# (an invalid function) and wasteful: counting them pushes the deployment past
# the Hobby plan's hard limit of 12 Serverless Functions, which fails the whole
# preview/production deploy. These suites run in CI (GitHub Actions), never on
# Vercel, so excluding them from the deployment has zero downside.
*.test.js
*.spec.js
